Interface ProviderData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Auditable, Resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FacebookProviderData, GithubProviderData, GoogleProviderData, LinkedInProviderData, SamlProviderData
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractProviderData, DefaultFacebookProviderData, DefaultGithubProviderData, DefaultGoogleProviderData, DefaultLinkedInProviderData, DefaultProviderData, DefaultSamlProviderData

    public interface ProviderData
extends Resource, Auditable
    Resource containing Provider-specific data for the Account. For example, for Google, it contains refreshToken and accessToken.
